        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Hot offers</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Gift boxes</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Projects</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">Menu item</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link nav-dropdown">Help
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <a href="#" class="nav-link nav-dropdown">English, USD
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link nav-dropdown">Ship to 🇩🇪
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </header>

  <div class="breadcrumb-bar">
    <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
      <a href="#">Home</a><span class="bc-sep">›</span>
      <a href="#">Clothings</a><span class="bc-sep">›</span>
      <a href="#">Men's wear</a><span class="bc-sep">›</span>
